        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Tom Sarbaugh is a bibliographer and historian of the air war in Spain. The collection includes his correspondence, most with Victor Berch of the ALBA archives, unpublished and published articles, bibliographies and bibliography cards, documents, lists, translations, most by Sarbaugh, some by others. Items by Sarbaugh include: "Spanish Civil War Aviators in Literature and Popular Fiction" and "Hidden History: Catalan Women Pilots for the Spanish Republic" (article, 1987).</p>
